OL,3,CKent carer says dementia patients "put
OL,4,Cto one side as if they no longer
OL,5,Cmatter"
OL,7,FA carer from Kent has spoken out
OL,8,Fagainst the government's decision to
OL,9,Fremove the dementia diagnosis target
OL,10,Fand says people with the condition are
OL,11,Fbeing "put to one side as if they no
OL,12,Flonger matter."
OL,14,FPaul Kemp from Rochester has been
OL,15,Fcaring for his wife, Sandra, for
OL,16,Fseveral years. She began to show
OL,17,Fsymptoms of early onset Alzheimer's
OL,18,Fwhen she was 51, but it took another
OL,19,Ftwo years for it to be confirmed.
