OL,3,CKent carer says dementia patients "put
OL,4,Cto one side as if they no longer
OL,5,Cmatter"
OL,7,F"it was just such a slow process" Paul
OL,8,Ftold us. "We started out with
OL,9,Fdepression apparently. I said it's not
OL,10,Fdepression there is something not
OL,11,Fright - and that is when the cycle of
OL,12,Fappointments started getting her
OL,13,Ftested. And, all the while, your life
OL,14,Fis just thrown all over the place."
OL,16,F"They're now going to kick it off and
OL,17,Fnot make it a priority - you can't do
OL,18,Fthat. This is one of the fastest
OL,19,Fgrowing ailments out there" he said.
