OL,5,Cmatter"
OL,7,FDementia is the biggest killer in the
OL,8,FUK and almost 1 in every 6 hospital
OL,9,Fbeds is occupied by someone living
OL,10,Fwith the condition.
OL,12,FThe diagnosis rate target, that 66.7%
OL,13,Fof people living with dementia in
OL,14,FEngland should have a diagnosis, has
OL,15,Fbeen removed from the NHS Operational
OL,16,FPlanning Guidance for the year.
