OL,3,CKent carer says dementia patients "put
OL,4,Cto one side as if they no longer
OL,5,Cmatter"
OL,7,FIn response, Fiona Carragher, Chief
OL,8,FPolicy and Research Officer at
OL,9,FAlzheimer's Society, said:
OL,10,F"Alzheimer's Society is shocked to
OL,11,Flearn that dementia, including a
OL,12,Fdementia diagnosis target, has been
OL,13,Fremoved from the NHS Operational
OL,14,FPlanning Guidance. This glaring
OL,15,Fomission is unacceptable and sends the
OL,16,Fmessage that dementia does not matter,
OL,17,Fand is not considered one of England's
OL,18,Fhealthcare priorities."
OL,26,@kD@cOUmD@GO]rD@AOU
