OL,3,CKent carer says dementia patients "put
OL,4,Cto one side as if they no longer
OL,5,Cmatter"
OL,7,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for the
OL,8,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,9,Fsaid:
OL,11,F"We inherited a broken NHS with too
OL,12,Fmany patients waiting far too long for
OL,13,Ftreatment.
OL,15,F"The dementia diagnosis target had not
OL,16,Fbeen met for half a decade, and the
OL,17,Fbest way to immediately make the NHS
OL,18,Fwork better for patients is to help
OL,19,Fleaders prioritise."
